certificates of origin, commercial invoices, and export licenses for garments shall include:

The issuance of a certificate of origin, commercial invoice, and license for export by air shall have the

following documents:
• Application for goods export of the interested company;
• Receipt issued by the Department of Administration;
• Certificate of Processing issued by the Ministry of Industry, Mines and Energy;
• Inspection Report of an official of the General System Preferences Department;
• Invoice of the company;
• Packing list of the company; and
• Sales contract between the purchaser and interested company.
